Commentary Text: J Suchith to Raina, out Caught by Dhawan!! Suchith has his man. But Raina has done his job. He resurrected the innings after a slow start and given them the impetus going into the final 5 overs. Commentary Text: Dwayne Bravo to J Suchith, out J Suchith Run Out!! Such has been the day for CSK today that even the least athletic fielder in their unit manages to break the stumps.
